      "order": 58
    },
    {
      "id": "mc_ordinaryMoments_009",
      "text": "比起盛大的告别，你会选择哪个平凡瞬间？",
      "topic": "ordinaryMoments",
      "order": 59
    },
    {
      "id": "mc_ordinaryMoments_010",
      "text": "当你想象日常会结束时，哪一部分显得神圣？",
      "topic": "ordinaryMoments",
      "order": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "mc_ordinaryMoments_011",
      "text": "你会想念什么？",
