      "text": "你希望所爱的人继续做什么，而且不带愧疚？",
      "topic": "peopleLeftBehind",
      "order": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "mc_peopleLeftBehind_009",
      "text": "当悲伤让人心碎时，你希望人们记得关于你的什么？",
      "topic": "peopleLeftBehind",
      "order": 101
    },
    {
      "id": "mc_peopleLeftBehind_010",
      "text": "你想让留下来的人知道，他们可以允许自己做什么？",
      "topic": "peopleLeftBehind",
      "order": 102
    },
    {
      "id": "mc_childrenMissedFutures_001",
